text: Stokeley Clevon Goulbourne (born April 18, 1996), known professionally as Ski Mask the Slump God â€“ formerly stylized as $ki Mask "The Slump God", is an American rapper and songwriter. ==Early life== Goulbourne was born in Fort Lauderdale, Florida. He is of Jamaican descent. His father was a rapper who used the stage name "Sin City". ==Career== He first became known for his work with XXXTentacion and their hip hop collective Members Only. His 2017 songs Catch Me Outside and Babywipe were certified gold by the Recording Industry Association of America (RIAA).
